    "description": "DXC Technology India Ventures Solutions has an exciting opening for a Backend Developer at our Vadodara office. Join a company that values innovation, collaboration, and continuous learning.\n\nAbout DXC Technology India Ventures Solutions:\nDXC Technology India Ventures Solutions is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Participate in on-call rotation for production support\n• Optimize application performance and ensure high availability\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n• Ensure code security and follow best practices for data protection\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n• Write clean, maintainable, and well-documented code\n• Contribute to system architecture and technical design decisions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in CI/CD\n• Proficiency in Docker\n• Proficiency in Go\n• Proficiency in Kubernetes\n• Proficiency in MongoDB\n• Proficiency in TypeScript\n• Proficiency in Agile/Scrum\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Vadodara, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with DXC Technology India Ventures Solutions!",
